    "chapter_title": {
      "ar": "بَابُ أَنَّ أَوَّلَ مَا خَلَقَ اللَّهُ مِنَ الْأَرَضِينَ مَوْضِعُ الْبَيْتِ وَ كَيْفَ كَانَ أَوَّلَ مَا خَلَقَ",
      "en": "Chapter 3 – The first of what Allah<sup>azwj</sup> Created from the lands was the place of the House (Kaaba), and how was the first of what He<sup>azwj</sup> Created"
